SELECT CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status, AVG(c.VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate
FROM CHARTEVENTS c
JOIN D_ITEMS d ON c.ITEMID = d.ITEMID
JOIN ICUSTAYS i ON c.STAY_ID = i.STAY_ID
JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON i.HADM_ID = a.HADM_ID
WHERE c.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND d.LABEL = 'Lactate' AND c.CHARTTIME BETWEEN i.INTIME AND i.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
GROUP BY CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END
rules.fixed_sql:
WITH lactate_events AS (
    SELECT c.HADM_ID, c.VALUENUM
    FROM CHARTEVENTS c
    JOIN D_ITEMS d ON c.ITEMID = d.ITEMID
    JOIN ICUSTAYS i ON c.STAY_ID = i.STAY_ID
    WHERE le.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND c.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL 
      AND d.LABEL = 'Lactate' 
      AND c.CHARTTIME BETWEEN i.INTIME AND i.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
),
patient_mortality AS (
    SELECT HADM_ID, CASE WHEN HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status
    FROM ADMISSIONS
)
SELECT pm.mortality_status, AVG(le.VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate
FROM lactate_events le
JOIN patient_mortality pm ON le.HADM_ID = pm.HADM_ID
GROUP BY pm.mortality_status
